public ActionException(String message,
                       LoggedAction source,
                       Exception exception)
Instantiates an ActionException with the specified message and source. It inherits fatal and print stack trace flags from the super class; and sets the inform user flag to false. Makes use of DeveloperException.DeveloperException(String).

source - the LoggedAction resulting in this error
